\cf0 \cb2 Saurabh Pant - BofA Securities, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Neil Mehta - Goldman Sachs Group, Inc., Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 John Anderson - Barclays Bank PLC, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Arun Jayaram - JPMorgan Chase & Co, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 James West - Melius Research LLC\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Stephen Gengaro - Stifel, Nicolaus & Company, Incorporated, Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Scott Gruber - Citigroup Inc., Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Derek Podhaizer - Piper Sandler & Co., Research Division\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb2 Marc Bianchi - TD Cowen, Research Division\cb1 \
